column5: anyone know how the roads are by crystal lake near Kinmount..thanks

Well if you mean access roads to get in you should be ok getting in there ??? its plowed and maintained all winter,there might be a few cottage roads that are not but,everything should be good to go,what is it you are after,fishing access????
was planning to do some walleye fishing but I have heard that that lake isn't very good at all....
What ever you do..... do not go to Camp Crystal Lake!!
Now TJ how can you say that about Jason and his Mom they run a fine camp for teens and their Hockey program is second to none.  Art
